{"type": "article", "id": 56565, "title": "一盏落地灯，轻轻一拨就能改变光源方向｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-19T22:51:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 47228, "name": "SKAGEN"}, {"id": 39082, "name": "Sèvres"}, {"id": 52877, "name": "Another Country"}, {"id": 52878, "name": "Ekkist"}, {"id": 21703, "name": "Frederik Roijé"}, {"id": 52879, "name": "Maysam Khankeshlou"}, {"id": 52880, "name": "Mohammad Amin Abbasszadeh"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 147, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180919211344tT1Z4NGXvk9Mxuh7.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s9 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Enso Light by Maysam Khankeshlou &amp; Mohammad Amin Abbasszadeh</h3><p>毕业于德黑兰艺术大学的工业设计师 Maysam Khankeshlou，最近与设计师 Mohammad Amin Abbasszadeh 合作，设计了一款名为 Enso 的落地灯。Enso 调整光源角度的方式很特别。</p><p>它有一个基座，顶部的圆形磁环，内嵌有一个自由移动的光源。用户可以手动将光源移动到磁环上的任何角度，由此产生的阴影和光束的动态变化，为落地灯添入灵动的味道。设计师试图通过这种手动改变光源方向的形式，强化与用户的互动关系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211428u7hmYdXICUe0KFf4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211428hCAT1tKsWbzlORUk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018091921142908OXrVRatf2dpBiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211430DA45dr0VuhkneMWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.340952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211430q2WuBcalLYJdVAP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/09/19/light-and-magnetism/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Height Width Chair by Frederik Roijé</h3><p>荷兰设计师 Frederik Roijé 的作品，常给人简单中蕴藏小惊喜的感觉。他把“简约”视为设计家具时的最重要的考虑元素。这把名为 Height Width 的座椅，就是一个结合了功能性和简约美学的代表作。</p><p>从名字不难看出，这把椅子的关键在于椅背，设计师试图在椅背的高度和宽度上做文章，做成舒适且可堆叠的椅子，适用于工作空间或是餐厅。粉末涂层钢框架和羊毛饰面的搭配，使其看起来精致美观，又符合极简主义调性。售价 445 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.roije.com/index.php?route=product%2Fproduct&amp;path=63_66&amp;product_id=239\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211523tBaKxAlU2LPmzIJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211523mp3vSUKktuIE8Bae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211524EOeUMvfLVJd08oTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809192115253TLBl0YDzNow2Eu7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211525ELCuW7e5rdZosckM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211526mVfCQMUSurp2lijY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ori Collection by Another Country </h3><p>英国家具设计工作室 Another Country 与设计机构 Ekkist 合作，制作了一系列围绕绿色环境、身体健康为主题的家具 Ori 系列，包括一个带有托盘的桌子、镜子和一张多用途沙发床等。</p><p>Ori 系列在今年的伦敦设计节上展出，展览名为 Designs for a Natural Home。 Ekkist 为整个系列的设计规定了一套设计指导原则，鼓励设计师在创作过程中考虑光线、水分、适应性和耐用性以及与周边环境的积极互动性。</p><p>Another Country 的设计师 Catherine Aitken 表示：“我们试图让这个系列在视觉上变得轻盈。”每件产品均采用可持续材料制成，包括灰木和有机 Kvadrat 纺织品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211559rgTQHe4X9WdKRa0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211559BSaK4U63A0PVpwgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211600rbtxg4ohBTuN5kld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211600ET8otpWJhwmc3GbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211601waqQHi3CGh9BRzYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211601gd6kqvQuZJ8fRixD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.327411\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/09/19/another-country-ekkist-ori-furniture-health-wellbeing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Falster Watch by SKAGEN</h3><p>SKAGEN 是由两个从哥本哈根来到美国创业的青年创立的时尚设计品牌。最近，他们在柏林国际电子消费展期间推出了第二代智能手表 Falster。它不仅更加简约、圆滑，透露出极简主义风格，而且性能上也更加智能。Falster 搭载 WearOS 系统，它具有心率监测、GPS 和 NFC 等功能。 </p><p>除了其性能的提升，外观方面，新款 Falster 仍然继承了丹麦品牌一贯的极简主义。更纤薄的表圈和 2 毫米的表壳，使 1.19 英寸的表盘看上去更大。</p><p>表冠一侧有两个自定义功能按钮，能让你快速开启指定的 app。为了强调个性化，用户可以挑选自己喜欢的表带，无论是金属、硅胶还是皮革。售价 275 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.skagen.com/en-us/wearable-technology/smartwatches\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211645wd8nhUckyBMJ3rbo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.338631\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211645MFZTOeY9cqsKHNwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.338631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211645HWTKCUqroP5zLs3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211645WixMkQ4Ar5bYXE6h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211646JGiSqCeFP8OrQt0v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809192116462qVLvcG0a6HAbDMU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211646a6MSNAcOzboHiVjk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Handle-flower by Nendo for Sèvres</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.qdaily.com/articles/56523.html\">昨天我们介绍了</a>创立于 1740 年的法国皇家御用瓷器品牌 Sèvres 推出的新品 hasu 桌。除了 hasu 桌之外，此系列还有一个手柄花系列，灵感主要来自 Sèvres 品牌中数目众多的茶杯和茶壶，而手柄花系列正是由这些器皿的把手制作而成的艺术品系列。</p><p>尺寸和形状不一的手柄共同组成一朵花的造型，并通过对花瓣数量、间隙和角度的调整来为每朵花赋予专属的特性。不同于创造新的形象，手柄花系列利用本身就具有独特历史意义的元素和形状为 Sèvres 品牌赋予了新的内涵。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211715JY8DjBsCmiAGwdpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211717302mG4CZrRL9KQh5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809192117151gAQLCjKiMeaXfE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211718Kghcd1EbNylR7SmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809192117180DHYgt9zkXbypCiB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180919211718YPQdIoW57Texs1ZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/handle-flower/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}